{
  "text": "That was precisely the point which I was trying to make. Thank you very much. Not to tie the instrument. I will just ask Ben if there's anything we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or to improve the contact. I am Ra. Please be aware that this instrument is somewhat fatigued. The channel is very clear. However we find the vital energy low. We do not wish to deplete the instrument. However, there is a shall we say energy exchange which we feel an honor, a duty to offer when this instrument opens itself. Therefore, counsel we this instrument to attempt to assess the vital energies carefully before offering itself as open channel. All is well. I leave this instrument and you in the love and in the light of the one infinite creator. Go forth then, rejoicing in the power and the peace of the one Creator Adnev.",
